{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Covid-secure certification to allow businesses to open during lockdowns",
        "additional_details": "Independent business owners keep our businesses covid secure because we care about keeping our customers, ourselves and our families, safe. We should be allowed to open if we offer a secure, clean environment.",
        "background": "The Government should create a system to allow all shops, particularly small independent businesses, to apply for a covid-secure certificate that allows them to stay open during the current and any future lockdowns. Local authorities could conduct spot checks to ensure businesses are opening safely.",
